SQL_STMT_U.val: Select A.ItemCode, A.PeriodCat, A.UsefulLife, A.RemainLife, B.OrDpAcc From ITM7 A Left Join ITM8 B On A.ItemCode = B.ItemCode And A.PeriodCat = B.PeriodCat Where A.ItemCode = ':1' And A.PeriodCat = ':2'
